      <title>波哥大缺水已持续数月，又面临断电风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-10/bogota-adds-risk-of-power-cuts-to-its-months-long-water-shortage</link>
      <description><![CDATA[哥伦比亚首都自 4 月份以来一直实行限水，可能不得不再次加强限制，由于新输电走廊建设推迟，目前该市还面临停电的风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-10/bogota-adds-risk-of-power-cuts-to-its-months-long-water-shortage</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Sep 2024 19:30:19 GMT</pubDate>
